Regeneration
------------

The list is embedded statically (go:embed) and ships with the app version; it is
NOT fetched at runtime (offline / privacy-preserving by design). To refresh it:

  1. Fetch MEW darklist:
     https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MyEtherWallet/ethereum-lists/master/src/addresses/addresses-darklist.json
     → take each entry's `address`.
  2. Fetch Revoke index.json, then each exploits/<name>.json:
     https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RevokeCash/approval-exploit-list/master/index.json
     → take each `addresses[].address`.
  3. Lowercase, trim, keep only valid 0x + 40-hex addresses, de-duplicate, sort.
  4. Write one address per line into malicious_spenders.txt (keep the header
     comment lines, which begin with '#').

